{"tid":1697953,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[HKDI 今晚要人] HKDI同學唔該入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T04:26:10.000Z","uid":187232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcf885cef9b52c3aa7e8228c9ba840d922ef1a5","tid":1697953,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTkQ0jc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTkQ0jc.jpg&h=f147e440&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnV9wrj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnV9wrj.jpg&h=dd4173b1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢一個星期HKDI都係會停課嘅關係，宣傳非常困難，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n赤腳與否係個人選擇, 不除鞋亦可參加, 一齊找尋真相 及 保護赤腳同路人<br />\n可自備電筒照明, 帶袋放鞋OR拖鞋 👟, 方便隨時走佬<br />\n1) 路徑大部份為單車徑和緩步跑徑, 少量石屎路<br />\n2) 海濱海岸絕大部份有工程進行, 海岸工程由大半年前開始至今未完工<br />\n3) 海岸工程附近道路有沙石<br />\n4) 小心留意路上沙石, 可減少受傷流血機會, 但不擔保可以完全不受傷流血<br />\n5) 路程約30-40分鐘<br />\n6) 赤腳步行的痛楚因人而異, 如中途不能承受可清潔後著鞋<br />\n*****有舉足輕重嘅疑點 同 線索, 不會在此說明, 請您除鞋行入去尋找*****<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好高興同大家講 youtuber 燒車亦會出席</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-KYCJ_y0SM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-KYCJ_y0SM8&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6796e338\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-KYCJ_y0SM8</a><br />\n時間7:30pm 於HKDI門口集合<br />\n先由小規模做起 赤腳人數限定30人, 請從速報名 <a href=\"https://t.me/standwithHKDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FstandwithHKDI&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9929e53a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/standwithHKDI</a><br />\n<br />\nHKDI再停課一個星期課好仆街<br />\n係咩用意真係唔洗講都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真相, 要用不同方法尋找, 要身體力行<br />\n香港人 同 HKDI同學請付出多一點, 你赤腳行嘅一少步, 將會係成功為彥霖伸冤嘅一大步"},{"pid":"c84fdb1920a1fc9a78980f859c1801b3d18a2a97","tid":1697953,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e474a328bead49c3b3ffaee4013aaeb46b4800d1","tid":1697953,"uid":112495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3c0ac76525ba8df73eb5949c5960aad0b72d3e","tid":1697953,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09b48223150cba9e4fe729a969d2f6e4f477fa37","tid":1697953,"uid":276319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"28c1b705e50b877f0f66d13b4989970d2b21c9ac","tid":1697953,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e373b13edb5615c8b1ebe6cecd8bf47c4657c4","tid":1697953,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14d083ca8ef5fa3948e8dfd8f352be3620fec552","tid":1697953,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim